  "body": "Example component:\r\n```javascript/jsx\r\n<div\r\n   style={{ width: 100, height: 100}}\r\n   onPointerDown={() => console.log(\"DOWN\")}\r\n   onPointerUp={() => console.log(\"UP\")}  // Does not fire with wacom pens!\r\n/>\r\n```\r\n\r\n**What is the current behavior?**\r\nas of v16.4.0, onPointerUp event fails to fire using wacom tablets.  (tested on Chrome, mac and windows).  In the past I used react-pointable that wrapped these functions, which also no longer works as of v16.4.0.",
